<head>Translation</head>
<p><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> of <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Dion</supplied>ysios Το<gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> and no-one <supplied reason="lost">else shall have the right to bury anyone here</supplied> <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> since whoever acts contrary to this provision <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> shall pay to the most sacred <supplied reason="abbreviation">Roman</supplied> treasury one thousand denarii of which <supplied reason="lost">a third shall go to the procurator</supplied> <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/></p>
